{"type": "article", "id": 3492, "title": "吸着雾霾看看雾霾主题海报展，也算是应景", "description": "设计师们希望用这些充满视觉震撼的海报唤起人们对于空气污染问题的重视。", "date": "2014-11-12T15:37:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4199, "name": "海报"}, {"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 4200, "name": "雾霾"}], "category": 17, "author": 1051, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607110528hBTwe0f6H9m45jSF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t昨日，APEC 会议进入最后一天，帝都人民喜得一整夜六级大风，让 APEC 蓝多少还能维持几天。但在这之后，北京又将进入群众苦盼风来模式。<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">而对于魔都及周边地区的人民来说，今天无疑是不幸的一天——PM 2.5 爆表达到 200 以上。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">自 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">2012 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">年年初那一场波及 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">17 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">省市的大范围雾霾开始，空气污染问题就成为每个中国人每天一睁眼就要忧虑的问题。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">世界自然基金会在一份研究报告中指出：“到 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">2030 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">年，人类的生存和发展环境将出现衰退”。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t最近，一群设计师们希望用富有创意的海报设计唤起人们对于空气污染问题的关注。 这项雾霾海报主题大赛<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">由全国 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">13 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">家协会于今年年初联合发起</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">，向全国设计师及创意人士征集雾霾主题海报，希望用作品发出中国设计师的公益声音。活动共收到了</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">3500 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">余幅海报，得到中央美院、清华美院等在内的 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">29 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">所高校的支持，最终由 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">9 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">位国际评委选出 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">295 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">幅优秀作品。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">近日，在浙江省科技馆针对其中 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">150 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">幅优秀作品进行展出。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t一起来看看这些创意十足的海报吧！张张都发人深省。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110522VAHC7g5qPrxEDZpc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6953125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110523pmMxzOb0EkCjve1P.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" align=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110523qwNyX24zxRHLaJgC.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" align=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69804401\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071105244HxlydDBOhwJAbFG.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" align=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69494585\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110524zctyUfm0VvujIYFh.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" align=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69437653\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110525DXvRu5Gmg3ToZfxq.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" align=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69070905\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071105255vGRcghVzlYtrZFK.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" align=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69804401\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110526zrHTeA3JgDcUphoR.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" align=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69559902\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110526pXDkI4h0AK8yiqm6.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" align=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110527OQ8bqyo0EVLYGnFx.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" align=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46332518\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110527dIB2w5gG7JF43LkS.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" align=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69559902\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}